trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser> control navigates to a new document whenever one of the following properties is set or methods is called: - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Url%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoHome%2A> - <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoSearch%2A> Handle the `DocumentCompleted` event to receive notification when the new document finishes loading.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser>Formant przechodzi do nowego dokumentu zawsze, gdy ustawiono jedną z następujących właściwości lub metody jest wywoływana:- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Url%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A>- <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A>— <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A>— <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A>— <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A>— <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoHome%2A>— <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoSearch%2A>obsługi `DocumentCompleted` zdarzeń, aby otrzymać powiadomienie, gdy nowy dokument zakończeniu ładowania.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoSearch%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoHome%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoForward%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.GoBack%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Navigate%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Url%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser>

trans-unit.source: When the `DocumentCompleted` event occurs, the new document is fully loaded, which means you can access its contents through the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A>, or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> property.
trans-unit.target: Gdy `DocumentCompleted` wystąpi zdarzenie, nowy dokument pełni został załadowany, co oznacza, że można uzyskać dostępu do jego zawartości za pośrednictwem <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A>, lub <xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A>Właściwości.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentStream%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.DocumentText%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.WebBrowser.Document%2A>

trans-unit.source: To receive notification before navigation starts, handle the <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebBrowserArray.Navigating> event.
trans-unit.target: Aby otrzymywać powiadomienia, zanim rozpocznie się nawigacji, obsługi <xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebBrowserArray.Navigating>zdarzeń.</xref:Microsoft.VisualBasic.Compatibility.VB6.WebBrowserArray.Navigating>

trans-unit.source: Handling this event lets you cancel navigation if certain conditions have not been met, for example, when the user has not completely filled out a form.
